author: The Critical Drinker
description: It was overlooked in its own time, never finding the audience it deserved, but Firefly has gone on to become a cult classic with the most dedicated on fanbases. And now that I've finally arrived to the party 20 years late, I wanted to share my thoughts on Joss Whedon's Firefly.
title: Firefly - We Didn't Know How Good We Had It
